These are Puzzles for 3x5 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x5-Level-4-1::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: puzzles, traveling, sudoku, camping, photography
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: horror, spy, thriller, time-travel, superhero
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: skiing, rowing, climbing, tennis, sailing
 1. the person watching horror movies is the person who's hobby is camping##1
 2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an even position##4
 3. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person who's sport is skiing##1
 4. the person who's sport is sailing is between the person watching horror movies and the person who's hobby is photography##2
 5. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 6. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 7. the person watching spy movies is on the far left##1
 8. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is photography##3
 9. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
10. the person watching superhero movies is the person who's sport is sailing##1
11. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
12. the person who's sport is climbing is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |      5      |
| Hobby         | traveling    | sudoku  | photography | puzzles    | camping |
| Movie-Genre   | spy     | thriller   | time-travel | superhero | horror   |
| Sport         | skiing | rowing | tennis  | sailing | climbing        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x5-Level-4-2::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: traveling, hiking, gardening, singing, puzzles
The people have 5 different jobs:  entrepreneur, nurse, paramedic, dancer, writer
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: skateboarding, climbing, ice-hockey, rowing, badminton
 1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is in an odd position##4
 2. the writer is between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the person who's sport is rowing##2
 3. the writer is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 5. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the nurse##1
 6. the person who's hobby is traveling is in the middle##1
 7. the entrepreneur is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 8. the nurse is on the far left##1
 9. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
10. the writer is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is traveling##3
11. the dancer is between the person who's sport is badminton and the person who's sport is climbing##2
12. the person who's sport is rowing is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1        |        2        |     3      |         4          |     5     |
| Hobby   | singing    | hiking         | traveling | puzzles        | gardening   |
| Job     | nurse | paramedic | dancer  | writer | entrepreneur |
| Sport   | ice-hockey       | badminton      | rowing   | climbing           | skateboarding      |

