.:: Puzzle 3x5-Level-4-3::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: sprite, milk, mirinda, 7up, hot-chocolate
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: volleyball, parkour, surfing, baseball, badminton
The people use 5 different means of transport: boat, car, van, quad-bike, bus
 1. the person drinking milk is the person who's sport is badminton##1
 2. the person driving the car is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 3. the person drinking 7up is in the middle##1
 4. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
 5. the person drinking sprite is between the person driving the car and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
 6. the person driving the van is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 8. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far right##1
 9. the person who's sport is baseball is in an even position##4
10. the person drinking mirinda is the person driving the bus##1
11. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person driving the van##1
12. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person who's sport is parkour and the person driving the bus##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |    2     |     3      |       4       |     5      |
| Beverage    | mirinda | milk    | 7up   | sprite          | hot-chocolate      |
| Sport       | surfing    | badminton | parkour       | baseball | volleyball |
| Transport   | bus     | quad-bike     | car | boat          | van     |

