.:: Puzzle 3x5-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: romance, musical, adventure, scientific, satire
5 different pets are kept: lizard, horse, goat, rabbit, turtle
The people use 5 different means of transport: quad-bike, bus, roller, train, scooter
 1. the person driving the bus is on the left or right of the owner of the goat##3
 2. the person driving the roller is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
 3. the person driving the bus is on the left or right of the person watching adventure movies##3
 4. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the owner of the horse##3
 5. the person watching musical movies is on the far right##1
 6. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the person watching romance movies##3
 7. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
 8. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person driving the train##1
 9. the owner of the turtle is in an even position##4
10. the person driving the scooter is in an odd position##4
11. the person watching romance movies is on the far left or far right##3
12. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |    3    |   4    |    5    |
| Movie-Genre   | romance     | satire    | adventure  | scientific | musical |
| Pet           | rabbit | horse    | goat | turtle  | lizard    |
| Transport     | scooter      | roller | train    | bus    | quad-bike    |

