.:: Puzzle 3x5-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: punk, blues, country, classical, hip-hop
There are 5 different nationalities: dutch, egyptian, colombian, indonesian, french
The people use 5 different means of transport: roller, subway, trike, bike, helicopter
 1. the person driving the subway is the fan of hip-hop##1
 2. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the fan of country##3
 3. the person driving the trike is in an even position##4
 4. the fan of hip-hop is the indonesian##1
 5. the person driving the bike is between the person driving the roller and the fan of hip-hop##2
 6. the fan of blues is in the middle##1
 7. the dutch is on the left of the egyptian##1
 8. the person driving the roller is on the right of the colombian##1
 9. the french is on the far right##1
10. the colombian is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
11. the fan of classical is the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |    5    |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop    | punk        | blues    | country      | classical  |
| Nationality   | indonesian | colombian    | dutch | egyptian | french |
| Transport     | subway   | bike | roller | trike      | helicopter   |

