 6. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
 7. the person drinking cola is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person drinking tea is in the middle##1
 9. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
10. the person driving the van is on the far left or far right##3
11. the fan of country is the person driving the motorbike##1
12. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the fan of rock##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |     4      |    5    |
