 3. the person who's hobby is singing is between the teacher and the person who's hobby is chess##2
 4. the pilot is on the left of the doctor##1
 5. the fan of electronic is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 6. the fan of disco is on the left or right of the security-guard##3
 7. the fan of disco is the person who's hobby is chess##1
 8. the fan of disco is on the right of the doctor##1
 9. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far left or far right##3
10. the fan of hip-hop is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |       4       |      5       |
| Hobby         | drawing | gardening | chess    | singing | baking      |
| Job           | pilot | doctor | chef | security-guard    | teacher |
| Music-Genre   | electronic        | d&b      | disco     | hip-hop          | dubstep        |

