.:: Puzzle 3x5-Level-4-9::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, 7up, iced-tea, coffee, tea
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: d&b, folk, dubstep, classical, electronic
5 different pets are kept: fish, dog, ferret, bird, guinea-pig
 1. the person drinking soy-milk is the fan of classical##1
 2. the fan of dubstep is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 3. the owner of the ferret is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 4. the owner of the dog is on the left of the fan of folk##1
 5. the owner of the ferret is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the fan of folk is the person drinking 7up##1
 7. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
 8. the owner of the fish is the person drinking 7up##1
 9. the fan of electronic is in an odd position##4
10. the owner of the guinea-pig is in an odd position##4
11. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |   3   |    4    |       5       |
| Beverage      | iced-tea  | soy-milk | 7up  | tea | coffee |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | classical       | folk | d&b | dubstep          |
| Pet           | ferret   | dog        | fish   | bird   | guinea-pig        |

