.:: Puzzle 3x5-Level-4-10::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  dancer, writer, project-manager, manager, engineer
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: martial-arts, disaster, spy, scientific, drama
5 different pets are kept: ferret, fish, frog, guinea-pig, bird
 1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the owner of the fish##3
 2. the project-manager is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
 3. the writer is in the middle##1
 4. the person watching spy movies is the manager##1
 5. the person watching drama movies is on the far right##1
 6. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 7. the owner of the ferret is in an odd position##4
 8. the owner of the fish is between the person watching disaster movies and the owner of the ferret##2
 9. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
10. the engineer is the person watching drama movies##1
11. the manager is on the left of the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |     4     |       5        |
| Job           | dancer | project-manager  | writer | manager | engineer |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | scientific | martial-arts     | spy    | drama        |
| Pet           | bird         | fish       | ferret | guinea-pig  | frog       |

