.:: Puzzle 3x5-Level-4-11::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, coffee, fanta, hot-chocolate, tea
There 5 different types of food: pumpkin, lemon, blueberry, cherry, cranberry
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: pop, gospel, reggae, soul, ambient
 1. the person eating pumpkin is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 2. the person drinking tea is the person eating blueberry##1
 3. the person eating blueberry is on the far right##1
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the fan of pop##1
 5. the fan of gospel is in an even position##4
 6. the fan of soul is on the left or right of the person eating cranberry##3
 7. the fan of pop is the person drinking fanta##1
 8. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person drinking tea and the fan of reggae##2
 9. the person eating cherry is in an odd position##4
10. the fan of soul is on the left of the person eating blueberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3      |   4    |   5   |
| Beverage      | fanta    | hot-chocolate | coffee   | iced-tea  | tea |
| Food          | cherry    | pumpkin  | cranberry | lemon | blueberry  |
| Music-Genre   | pop | gospel    | reggae      | soul   | ambient |

