 6. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
 7. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
 8. the person eating spinach is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far right##1
10. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
