 4. the spanish is on the left or right of the american##3
 5. the indian is the bartender##1
 6. the accountant is the person driving the bike##1
 7. the person driving the tram is between the entrepreneur and the accountant##2
 8. the entrepreneur is the person driving the car##1
 9. the spanish is the person driving the tram##1
10. the japanese is the person driving the bike##1
11. the american is in an odd position##4
12. the american is the entrepreneur##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |     3     |         4          |     5     |
| Job           | entrepreneur | architect | accountant    | chef | bartender  |
| Nationality   | american     | spanish    | japanese  | turkish              | indian |
| Transport     | car     | tram       | bike | train         | snowmobile    |

