 6. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left or right of the argentine##3
 7. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 8. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is badminton##3
 9. the person who's sport is badminton is between the person who's sport is sailing and the person who's sport is rowing##2
10. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the argentine##1
11. the person who's sport is golf is in an odd position##4
